        public java.lang.String toPredictiveCodedXML(PassSuccessPrediction iNode)
        Description copied from class: Node
        This method is used to create the corresponding predictive-coded xml output (on P-Frames). The data is not encoded like it is by P-Frames in pictures. The original Node will only be compared to this Node and all changed fields are written into the xml String (not the difference between the original value and new value!)
